      • selectValue

        public static void selectValue(com.google.gwt.user.client.ui.ListBox listBox,
               java.lang.String value)
        Sets the value in the List Box. Traverse the listBox and select the option whose value matches the value.
        Parameters:
        listBox - ListBox listBox in which value is to be selected. If Null, request is bypassed.
        value - String Value of the item to be selected.
